xt":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"For example, you can track attendance for an event by adding the tag “RSVP-Blood Drive-Event date” to anyone who RSVPs on your event page.\u0026nbsp;","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"video","provider":"youtube","id":"TCQEY7OW1uw"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Under \u003cb\u003e[Page Type] Settings\u003c/b\u003e, type your tag(s) into the box labelled \"Tag [XX] with.\" In this example, I am assigning all of the people who RSVP'd to my blood drive with the tag \"RSVP-blood drive-Feb 19.\" Make sure to separate multiple tags with commas. Click \u003cb\u003eSave settings\u003c/b\u003e.","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Once this tag is set up and people have signed up online, you will be able to see this tag on their profile.\u0026nbsp;","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"image","url":"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/180757489/b50adb84ed92717bafa770bd/Screen+Shot+2020-01-29+at+3.53.33+PM.png","width":2456,"height":820},{"type":"paragraph","text":"You can also \u003ca href=\"https://nationbuilder.com/how_to_filter\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003efilter\u003c/a\u003e for the tag and find all of the people with it. ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"image","url":"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/180757876/35d220438ae89617a1358513/Screen+Shot+2020-01-29+at+3.58.14+PM.png","width":2470,"height":1272},{"type":"heading","text":"Assign a point person","idAttribute":"assign-a-point-person"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Assigning a point person when a visitor takes an action on your website is key. A point person is responsible for that visitor’s relationship with your organization.","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"For example, your volunteer coordinator would be an excellent point person for people who sign up on your volunteer page. Any \u003ca href=\"https://support.nationbuilder.com/settings/your-account/manage-control-panel-users\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003econtrol panel user\u003c/a\u003e can be listed as a point person. ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"video","provider":"youtube","id":"6D3f4LnEXuo"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Under \u003cb\u003e[Page Type] Settings\u003c/b\u003e, select one of your control panel users from the dropdown menu labelled \"Point person.\" Click \u003cb\u003eSave settings. \u003c/b\u003eNote that if a visitor already has a point person, they will not be assigned a new one when they take a website action.","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Now, once the point person is set and people have signed up online, you will see people's profiles with the name of the point person on them.\u0026nbsp;","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"image","url":"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/180758332/71b89720a6b6163b6ec6224b/Screen+Shot+2020-01-29+at+4.01.37+PM.png","width":2370,"height":580},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Just as you saw above for tags, you can \u003ca href=\"https://support.nationbuilder.com/people/target-people/how-to-target-people\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003efilter\u003c/a\u003e by point person to see all of the people assigned to that person. ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"image","url":"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/180758578/eafdf3635834a80f3428fccf/Screen+Shot+2020-01-29+at+4.03.16+PM.png","width":2468,"height":1234},{"type":"heading","text":"Add a supporter to a path","idAttribute":"add-a-supporter-to-a-path"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"It's a good idea to \u003ca href=\"https://support.nationbuilder.com/people/basics/create-a-path\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eadd a supporter to a path\u003c/a\u003e. A path is a step-by-step workflow that describes how people taking action contribute toward achieving a larger goal. Paths allow you to build and \u003ca href=\"https://support.nationbuilder.com/people/gather-profiles/tracking-relationships\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003etrack relationships with your supporters\u003c/a\u003e. ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"video","provider":"youtube","id":"OTvWyCk7Ojs"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Under \u003cb\u003e[Page Type] Settings\u003c/b\u003e, check “Add to path” and add the appropriate information: path (e.g. \"Become a donor\"), path assigned to (overall point person), step (a specific step on a path), step point person (if different from the overall path point person), and step due date (optional). Click \u003cb\u003eSave settings\u003c/b\u003e.","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Once someone takes the action and is added to a path, the path will display on their profile and you can view how far along on that path they are.\u0026nbsp;","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"image","url":"https://downloads.intercomcdn.com/i/o/111487079/6c4cb84f16194fae86481faf/Screen_Shot_2019-03-27_at_9_32_18_AM.png","width":1078,"height":479},{"type":"paragraph","text":"You also can \u003ca href=\"https://support.nationbuilder.com/people/target-people/how-to-target-people\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003efilter\u003c/a\u003e to find people on specific paths, completed paths, abandoned paths, etc. ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"paragraph","text":" ","class":"no-margin"},{"type":"image","url":"https://downloads.intercomcdn